{"tid":853741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劏房男疑殺人燒屋跳樓亡","createTime":"2018-10-08T23:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T01:02:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"04600999d9b110506a1402a4a1a3406d82f55e19","tid":853741,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T23:51:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181009/20518195\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181009%2F20518195&d=CibHFg8IZnIlajm27DXBW%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=eb1ef67b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181009%2F20518195&h=3fa53f51\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181009/20518195</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月09日 <br />\n<br />\n劏房男疑殺人燒屋跳樓亡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181009/large/09la5p90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181009%2Flarge%2F09la5p90.jpg&h=39c2aeb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消防員到火警單位內開喉灌救。唐家輝攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】深水埗大南街昨晚發生雙屍命案，一名男子與人爭執後跳樓喪生，其劏房住所疑被縱火，消防員到場將火救熄後，在火場發現一具男性屍體，警方懷疑死因有可疑，正調查兩案是否有關連，不排除有人殺人後畏罪縱火跳樓亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181009/large/09la5p91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181009%2Flarge%2F09la5p91.jpg&h=f568ae28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大批唐樓住客疏散到地面。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n單位內發現男屍<br />\n<br />\n墮樓死者68歲，租住深水埗大南街214至216號唐樓頂樓一個一劏四劏房單位，另一死者屍身沒被燒焦，但身有刀傷，身份不明，未知是否劏房住客。據街坊稱，其中一名死者懷疑姓周，從事裝修，數月前其內地妻子持單程證來港，事發前返鄉探親未返。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚11時53分，街坊稱出事單位傳來爭吵聲，未幾發現劏房單位發生火警，及後見一名男子從唐樓高處墮下，街坊立即報警。警員及消防救護員到場，將墮樓男子送廣華醫院搶救，證實不治。消防員進入火場救火，16分鐘後將火救熄，並在火場內發現一具男性屍體。<br />\n<br />\n■記者江寶龍、唐家輝  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n警長供稱曾打死者屁股<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n苦戀已婚老闆女工揮剪　工場內攀窗尋死警破門救人"},{"pid":"4bc81765c5469e6abb733d2837a499da43edf6df","tid":853741,"uid":75232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T23:58:36.000Z","msg":"俾人斬嗰個食咗人老婆，之後武大郎斬人縱火然後跳樓？"},{"pid":"81c9e1dfb6698ea32e473c3c2ae1d3dde4f30e27","tid":853741,"uid":3457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T00:00:02.000Z","msg":"內地女人 知咩原因喇😂"},{"pid":"9151241cfcfca20316ae80f78c07de47f017c2b9","tid":853741,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T00:02:51.000Z","msg":"點解唔燒全層？"},{"pid":"ab1605cb63c19937a10d2a77ef4d8382494a4b20","tid":853741,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T00:02:58.000Z","msg":"支那女人<br />\n老公自殺<br />\n<br />\n特快上樓<br />\n安排同鄉來港<br />\n享多重福利<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1b93e3ae7fa7a4b53df3ff77509169998ad016","tid":853741,"uid":144774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T00:03:27.000Z","msg":"又係乂陸婆"},{"pid":"774210f573875d8e2abe56b4d1193c4afee9a0dd","tid":853741,"uid":144774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T00:03:41.000Z","msg":"大陸婆"},{"pid":"6a4e7b29448bfbcfba67cd5735dd5b4638680b29","tid":853741,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T00:06:30.000Z","msg":"笑公屋仔嗰班五毛狗去撚晒邊?"},{"pid":"a03f148d2467e548a80baf201c3c0e04f7061d7e","tid":853741,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T00:33:21.000Z","msg":"一不做二不休"},{"pid":"f5087072e25d58fc60a8eba6969f021da26f63f9","tid":853741,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T00:35:06.000Z","msg":"經濟一差會日日見到"},{"pid":"e770bd98897b903adada72bf5ba5cd9d05abd0fe","tid":853741,"uid":29093,"li